<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Order Confirmation - Ilan Shop</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        color: #1a202c;
    }
    a {
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
        color: #764ba2;
    }
    .email-container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    .email-header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        padding: 50px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
    }
    .success-badge {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .checkmark {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        position: relative;
    }
    .checkmark:after {
        content: '‚úì';
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        color: white;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .email-header p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .email-body {
        padding: 40px;
    }
    .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .greeting strong {
        color: #667eea;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .section-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #1a202c;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 30px 0 20px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .order-items {
        background: #f7fafc;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .order-item {
        display: flex;
        padding: 15px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .order-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .order-item:first-child {
        padding-top: 0;
    }
    .item-image-placeholder {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-right: 15px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .item-details {
        flex: 1;
    }
    .item-name {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a202c;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .item-meta {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #718096;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .item-options {
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .option-badge {
        background: #edf2f7;
        color: #4a5568;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .item-price {
        text-align: right;
        padding-left: 15px;
    }
    .item-unit-price {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #718096;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .item-total-price {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #667eea;
    }
    .order-summary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        color: white;
    }
    .summary-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 12px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    .summary-total {
        border-top: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding-top: 15px;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
    }
    .info-box {
        background: #f7fafc;
        border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .info-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .email-footer {
        background: #f7fafc;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer-text {
        color: #718096;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer-links {
        margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer-links a {
        color: #667eea;
        margin: 0 15px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .social-links {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .social-links a {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        background: #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 5px;
        line-height: 36px;
        color: #667eea;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .social-links a:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .copyright {
        color: #a0aec0;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
            padding: 20px 10px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 25px 20px;
        }
        .email-header {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
        }
        .order-item {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .item-price {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="success-badge">
                <div class="checkmark"></div>
            </div>
            <h1>Order Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for shopping with us</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="email-body">
            <p class="greeting">
                Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Great news! Your order has been confirmed and is now being prepared for shipment. 
                We'll notify you as soon as it's on its way.
            </p>

            <h2 class="section-title">üì¶ Order Details</h2>
            
            <div class="order-items">
                <% cart.forEach(function(item, index) { %>
                <div class="order-item">
                    <div class="item-image-placeholder">
                        <%= (item.title || 'P').charAt(0).toUpperCase() %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-details">
                        <div class="item-name"><%= item.title || 'Product' %></div>
                        <div class="item-meta">
                            Quantity: <%= item.quantity %>
                        </div>
                        <% if (item.selectedOptions && Object.keys(item.selectedOptions).length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="item-options">
                            <% if (item.selectedOptions.color) { %>
                            <span class="option-badge">üé® <%= item.selectedOptions.color %></span>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (item.selectedOptions.size) { %>
                            <span class="option-badge">üìè <%= item.selectedOptions.size %></span>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-price">
                        <div class="item-unit-price">
                            $<%= item.sale_price.toFixed(2) %> each
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-total-price">
                            $<%= (item.quantity * item.sale_price).toFixed(2) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>

            <div class="order-summary">
                <div class="summary-row summary-total">
                    <span>Total Amount</span>
                    <span>$<%= totalAmount.toFixed(2) %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p>
                    <strong>üì¨ What's next?</strong><br>
                    We're currently processing your order. You'll receive a shipping confirmation email 
                    with tracking information once your items are on their way to you.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    üîç Track Your Order
                </a>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    Need help with your order? We're here for you!
                </p>
                <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px;">
                    Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ilan.com">support@ilan.com</a> 
                    or visit our <a href="https://ilan.com/help">Help Center</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                <strong>Thank you for choosing Ilan!</strong><br>
                We appreciate your business and hope you love your purchase.
            </p>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="https://ilan.com/shop">Continue Shopping</a>
                <a href="https://ilan.com/orders">My Orders</a>
                <a href="https://ilan.com/help">Help Center</a>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://facebook.com/ilan">f</a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/ilan">ùïè</a>
                <a href="https://instagram.com/ilan">üì∑</a>
            </div>

            <p class="copyright">
                ¬© 2025 Ilan Shop. All rights reserved.<br>
                123 Commerce Street, City, Country
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>